## ğŸ¯ What is Navam Invest?

**Replace $1,000-$10,000/year wealth management fees with AI agents that research, analyze, and explain investment decisions in plain English.**

Navam Invest is an **open-source AI investment advisory platform** designed for retail investors managing $50K-$1M portfolios. Instead of paying 1% AUM fees, you get a **team of 7 specialized AI agents** that collaborate through multi-agent workflowsâ€”all running locally with your API keys, using free public data.

